// Divide-and-conquer statergy or approach yeh hai ki koi problem badi hai hai ya mtlb lambi hai. Then uss problem ko divide karo mtlb break kro and then unn tukdo ko solve kro. And atlast unn sbhi tukdo k results ko combine krdo or sumup krdo to get the actual whole solution.

